	abstract = {Composition, abundance, and diversity of peracarids (Crustacea) were investigated over a period of 3 mo in the Northeast Water Polynya (NEW), off Greenland. Samples were collected from May to July 1993 during expeditions ARK IX/2 and 3 using an epibenthic
